name: Blue Headgear
description:
A woman of mystery, looking as if she just stepped out of the 1920s. Is she headed to a Hollywood premier, or out for a night of drinks at the Brown Derby? She is glamorous, beautiful, clad in a mask that compels all who see her to whisper, "stunning."

Her blue mask fiercely protects her, her eyes convey her openness to experiencing life, her jewels proclaim her to be a woman of means. She is, simply, the woman in the blue headgear.
